code: export default function getCookie(cname){var name=cname+"=";var decodedCookie=decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);var ca=decodedCookie.split(";");for(var i=0;i<ca.length;i++){var c=ca[i];while(c.charAt(0)===" "){c=c.substring(1);}if(c.indexOf(name)===0){return c.substring(name.length,c.length);}}return"";}
